title: My name is not in Oceanic Reef Plaque

replies.body:
Hey there,

If your name isn't on the list it's pretty safe to assume you didn't earn enough points in time during the event, it was over pretty quick thus there were a lot of people who thought they had enough points but in reality didn't earn them in time.

It's also possible you're getting the most recent event confused with the 2015 (nautilus reef) event.

If you've changed your summoner name at all I'd check to see if any of your old summoner names are on the list, just to be sure.

Hi My summoner name is not on the the oceanic week statue even tho i scored up to 20 points in that week and  all my friend i did it with dont have there names on there ether ? can you please CHECK  THIS
You're thinking of the wrong event. This one went for like 2 days. If you got 20 wins in 2 days seek help or sunshine lol.
My name is also not there even though i got the free champ. Can someone look into this?

Same here. Earned a ton of points because I partied up with a bunch of friends IRL as a mini event for something to do. Their names are on it but not mine. I can understand if they want to not include offensive names but Flaming Scrotum is there but not Flaming Meat.
